    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and is further protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains soft and matte, the buttons show zero wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the smallest interior light, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
